  <sect2 role="package">
    <title>Introduction to c-ares</title>

    <para>
      <application>c-ares</application> is a C library for asynchronous DNS
      requests.
    </para>

    &lfs91_checked;

    <bridgehead renderas="sect3">Package Information</bridgehead>
    <itemizedlist spacing="compact">
